程序包 com.google.typography.font.sfntly

类 Tag

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.typography.font.sfntly.Tag
  • public final class Tag
extends java.lang.Object
    Font identification tags used for tables, features, etc. Tag names are consistent with the OpenType and sfnt specs.
    作者:
    Stuart Gill

        public static boolean isHeaderTable​(int tag)
        Determines whether the tag is that for the header table.
        参数:
        tag - table tag
        返回:
        true if the tag represents the font header table
